Given the player's action description, determine if it is a combat action
and identify the targets.

===== PLAYER =====
Name: {{ player.name }}
Level: {{ player.level | default(1) }}
{% if player.weapon_ids %}Weapons: {{ player.weapon_ids | join(', ') }}{% endif %}

===== PEOPLE PRESENT =====
